data.title: Birth Certificate
meta_keywords: St. Louis County Minnesota Birth Certificate
data.meta_description: How to order or amend a Birth Certificate in person, by mail, fax or email from St. Louis County Minnesota
data.text:
An Individual must have Tangible Interest to obtain a birth certificate. Some birth certificates are confidential and can only be released to certain individuals or the parent on the record.

Birth Certificate Fee Information

1 Certified Copy - $26.00

1 Non-Certified Copy - $13.00

Each additional copy of the same certified record purchased at the same time - $19.00. Each additional copy of the same non-certified record purchased at the same time - $6.00.

◾Make your check or money order payable to the St. Louis County Recorder.

◾United States of America Currency only.
